    "description": "Lexar Media introduces JumpDrive SAFE S3000, the world's first FIPS 140-2 Level 3 approved secure USB flash drive. The advanced flash drive combines an onboard cryptographic controller that encrypts all data stored on the secure partition by approved hardware-based AES 256bit, a smartcard chip that provides key management through proven technology, and a ruggedized tamper resistant housing to create a complete portable secure storage solution for all users looking to protect their data. For more information please visit http://www.lexar.com.",
